Interface ProfileContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ProfileContainer
    Interface for the profile container. User-defined version should be inherited from AbstractProfileContainer

    • Method Detail

      • setProfileListener

        void setProfileListener(ProfileListener listener)
        Set Kaa profile listener ProfileListener for the container. DO NOT use this API explicitly. When user sets his implementation of the profile container, Kaa uses this method to inject its own listener DefaultProfileListener.
        Parameters:
        listener - Listener that tracks profile updates
